Paper: hep-th/0006216

Date: 2000-06-28

Title: Fermion doubling problem and noncommutative geometry II

Authors: A. P. Balachandran, T. R. Govindarajan, B. Ydri

Comments: 8 pages, LATEX2e

In our previous paper (hep-th/9911087), we proposed a resolution for thefermion doubling problem in discrete field theories based on the fuzzy sphereand its cartesian products. In this paper after a review of that work, we bringout its relationship to the Ginsparg-Wilson approach.